act:
1330088 THE MERCHANT SHIPPING (AMENDMENT) ACT, 2002
ACT NO. 63 OF 2002 [ 17th December, 2002.]
An Act further to amend the Merchant Shipping Act, 1958, and the Major Port Trusts Act, 1963.
BE it enacted by Parliament in the Fifty- third Year of the Republic of India as follows:-
CHAP
PRELIMINARY
CHAPTER I
PRELIMINARY
865958 1 Short title and commencement.-
786357 1This Act may be called the Merchant Shipping (Amendment) Act, 2002.
852829 2It shall come into force on such date as the Central Government may, by notification in the Official Gazette, appoint and different dates may be appointed for different provisions of this Act. CHAP
AMENDMENT OF THE MERCHANT SHIPPING ACT, 1958
