1027446 afor sub- section (4), the following sub- section shall be substituted, namely:- " (4) When any incident involving two or more ships occurs and pollution damage results therefrom, the owners of all the ships concerned, unless exonerated under sub- section (3), shall be jointly separable."; and severally liable for such damage which is not reasonabl
